# Test: Student Registration - Vanilla JS + Tailwind
# URL: https://testrpages.com/vanilla-tailwind/good
# Tags: smoke, registration, form

Navigate to https://testrpages.com/vanilla-tailwind/good
Wait for 2 seconds
Verify that the page contains "Student Registration"
Click on the Register Student link
Type "James" in the First name input field
Type "Anderson" in the Last name input field
Select "Female" from the Gender dropdown
Select "High School" from the Grade dropdown
Type "A passionate student who loves science and mathematics." in the Student Personal Statement textarea

Type "Robert Anderson" in the Parent Name input field
Type "robert.anderson@email.com" in the Email input field
Type "0412345678" in the Phone input field
Type "42 Wallaby Way, Sydney NSW 2000" in the Address textarea

Take a screenshot named "vanilla-form-filled"

Click the Submit Application button
Wait for 2 seconds
Take a screenshot named "vanilla-form-submitted"